title: Just for Kicks
overview: Just for Kicks brings together a diverse range of guests to discuss their most exciting shoe stories and reveal the reasons behind some of the boldest fashion choices we've ever seen. The series will feature a range of games and challenges like never before that are sure to stump even the most confident shoe aficionados. Just for Kicks will also feature interviews with celebrities from across sports, movies, and music. World-famous DJ Whoo Kid, who will do more than play music - while comedian and host Wayne Young will keep the audience involved as the MC of the party.
